
Key files:
* Main.tex - top level WSU System Design Description file
* WSU-Processes.tex - description of planned and expected operational processes in WSU operations.
     of particular relevance is the "Data Processing and Quality Assurance" section
* WSU-DataProperties.tex - the appendix that describes in detail the projected
     WSU data properties, in comparison to current properties. The main 
     results are presented in tabular format in these files:
       *tables/data_prop_summ.tex
       *tables/table_data_prop.tex
       *tables/table_data_rate_peak.tex
       *tables/table_data_rates_prop.tex
       *tables/table_system_performance_blc.tex
       *tables/table_system_performance_wsu.tex

